dct_description_sm: Map shows: International, provincial, divisional, and district boundaries; divisional headquarters; roads and rivers; native courts; native administration schools and dressers; headquarters mission station, Basle M., R C M., Baptist; government medical stations; Roman Catholic catechumenates; government, vernacular, and mission schools. Original map is filed in the Map/Geospatial Center, a map reproduction is attached to companion volume. "P.3554,9541.A2491,808,875,8/30."
